1
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:17,879
Your return has caused this land to
revive.

2
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:19,239
Triggering changes in the heavens.

3
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:22,119
[Previously]
This is the other shore of the River
of Time.

4
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,359
Is that you, Huang?

5
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,999
What exactly happened?

6
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:28,479
Finally, we've waited for the treasure
to emerge.

7
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:31,359
Invite Ancient Ancestors Yu Tuo and
An Lan to descend.

8
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,239
That direction...

9
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:35,439
Could it be where Huang went?

10
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:00,959
This ancient land can actually block
the aftershocks of the Ancient Ancestors.

11
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,999
It's fine that we are unharmed,

12
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:06,479
but how is this trash still alive?

13
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,439
The Foreign Realm has gone to such
great lengths...

14
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,519
this item must be of great importance.

15
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:16,399
But he got it in the end.

16
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:17,800
What a pity.

17
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,839
Ancient Ancestor, be careful!

18
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,959
Creatures from the Burial Grounds
are attacking!

19
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,719
Recognizing thieves as fathers.

20
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,279
What loyalty, you slave.

21
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,279
You fawn over your new master more
eagerly than anyone.

22
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,239
One day, I will take your head

23
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,239
and dig out the rebellious bone
behind your skull.

24
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,400
Impudent!

25
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,799
That Burial King didn't care about
the rotten wooden chest at all.

26
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:02,519
He came solely to block Ancient Ancestor
Yu Tuo.

27
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:06,479
Could it be because this object emerged
from the burial grounds?

28
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,879
He doesn't want to be dragged into
this mess.

29
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,959
Stop yapping.

30
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,040
Look!

31
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,279
The Ancient Ancestor's dharma body
is disintegrating.

32
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,519
Our retreat is in danger.

33
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,559
If we drag this out,

34
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,119
we won't be able to bring the chest
back.

35
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,439
These two old jade bastards...

36
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,359
they are ultimately restricted by
the Abyss of Heaven.

37
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,719
Their true bodies can't descend.

38
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,399
A projected dharma body

39
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:28,959
probably won't last much longer.

40
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,319
Ancient Ancestor An Lan has come to
assist!

41
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,399
What is that thing?

42
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,399
Could it be the King of the Burial
Grounds?

43
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,720
Old Burial once said,

44
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,959
some peerless burial attendants can
shed their deathly aura.

45
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,799
Their descendants become Golden Burial
Attendants.

46
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,359
But some powerhouses remain in the
ominous lands,

47
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:10,959
surrounded by billowing dead mist.

48
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,119
The one before us is likely the latter.

49
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,480
You...

50
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:37,279
Do you think my true body cannot come
here?

51
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,240
Everyone, don't panic.

52
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,320
As the Great Elder said,

53
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,520
as long as the Tian Yuan (Abyss of
Heaven) is unbroken,

54
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,039
it is the greatest barrier for the
Imperial Pass.

55
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,319
We just need to hold our ground.

56
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,560
Do not throw ourselves into chaos.

57
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,919
The Tian Yuan has been disturbed.

58
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,999
It is shaking off the Burial King,

59
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,559
and also blocking the descent of An
Lan and Yu Tuo's true bodies.

60
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,799
It is Yu Tuo Ancient Ancestor's Time
Imprint.

61
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,399
It only affects a single instant.

62
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,919
It will dissipate after one strike.

63
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,719
But if we can buy a sliver of opportunity,

64
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:46,279
perhaps Ancient Ancestor An Lan can
still seize the treasure.

65
00:06:46,303 --> 00:07:07,903
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

66
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,439
Two Ancient Ancestors...

67
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,439
Failed.

68
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:16,119
This branch of the burial ground
is within the border wilderness.

69
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,559
Once this Burial King loses control
and goes mad,

70
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,999
it will surely threaten the Imperial
Pass.

71
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:37,039
Since it is a treasure contested by
Immortal Kings,

72
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,679
it must be entangled with strangeness.

73
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,199
Once fluctuations erupt,

74
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,159
it might turn people into pools of
blood instantly.

75
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,839
They don't dare to act recklessly either.

76
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,839
The situation was perilous just now.

77
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,999
Yet you remained quite composed.

78
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,679
Compared to those wastes,

79
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,159
you have some redeeming qualities.

80
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,439
This chest is bizarre.

81
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,479
Anyone acting alone might fall into
a trap.

82
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,879
For the grand plan of our realm,

83
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,200
how about we temporarily ally

84
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,280
to take it first?

85
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,920
After securing it,

86
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,719
we can compete based on our own abilities.

87
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,200
How about it?

88
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,239
Why are you dragging your feet?

89
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,639
One word:

90
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:22,319
Are we doing this or not?

91
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,999
If you don't, plenty of others will.

92
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,479
To be frank,

93
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,040
to have gotten this far,

94
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,159
both of us have made contributions.

95
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,879
We are merely contending for priority.

96
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,439
Since you have doubts,

97
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,240
how about...

98
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,359
Don't thank me.

99
00:08:43,680 --> 00:08:44,680
For the sake of the Ancient Ancestors,

100
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,679
I am willing to use the blood of the
Imperial Clan as a covenant.

101
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,679
Listen carefully:

102
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,679
Today, we shall jointly retrieve the
wooden chest.

103
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,639
Neither party shall harm the other
during the process.

104
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,519
Should anyone violate this oath,

105
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,679
their spirit and form shall be

106
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,280
annihilated.

107
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,239
Completely unharmed?

108
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,079
You clearly came prepared.

109
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,759
I knew something was off.

110
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,199
You invited me to get close,

111
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,839
how could I refuse such kindness?

112
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,479
Perfect chance to settle everything
at once.

113
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,880
It's you!

114
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:24,799
Huang!

115
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,439
You dare to secretly learn the taboo
secret arts of my realm's Imperial
Clan!

116
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,479
A rebellious lineage that has knelt
for too long,

117
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,519
forgetting your own origins,

118
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,199
truly treating the Foreign Realm as
your ancestral soil.

119
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:37,039
My clan long ago fought its way out
of the Nine Heavens.

120
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,639
You, dogs of a defeated clan,

121
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,720
have only death awaiting you.

122
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,959
Today, I shall slay you to establish
my name!

123
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,919
No backlash.

124
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,919
I can directly seize that chest.

125
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:18,919
Huang,

126
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,959
do you really think you are invincible?

127
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,439
Using my ancestral arts to seal this
place,

128
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,359
you have no escape.

129
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,280
Get lost!

130
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:38,639
Slay him!

131
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:39,839
I alone am enough.

132
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,080
Arrogant!

133
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:43,959
Watch as I kill every single one of
you!

134
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:06,359
So the Skull Fruit had something to
do with this anomaly after all.

135
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,599
Fortunately,

136
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,319
it wasn't an issue with the chest
itself.

137
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,479
This chest used to move on its own.

138
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,999
Don't even think about leaving.

139
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,879
So this Undying Medicine didn't just
want to use me as a weapon,

140
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,479
it wanted to take the treasure too.

141
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,320
Hey!

142
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,599
If you don't leave that chest,

143
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,959
I'll stew you for sure!

144
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,719
Let's see how far you can run this
time.

145
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,000
What the hell is this place?

146
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,639
We accidentally entered a branch of
the burial grounds.

147
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,439
Good thing we didn't barge into a den
of burial attendants.

148
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:00,079
Otherwise, we'd be in deep trouble.

149
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:23,039
Speak of the devil, and he appears.

150
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:42,399
Out of the wolf's den and into the
tiger's lair.

151
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,159
Identity exposed.

152
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:47,479
You will be refined into a burial slave
by the Golden Burial Attendants.

153
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,599
Worse than death.

154
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:51,799
And I'm going to be made into coffin
planks for the Burial King.

155
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,039
Don't panic when trouble arises.

156
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,000
If we cooperate,

157
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,199
pretending to be Golden Burial Attendants
might buy us time.

158
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,559
There's a chance we can get out of
this.

159
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:07,359
Yeah, right, I trust you.

160
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,879
These vengeful spirits are already at
the Dun Yi (Escape One) Realm.

161
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,999
How could they not tell I'm a plant?

162
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:13,880
Become my divine pet.

163
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:16,359
Use your primordial spirit to teach
me the Ancient Burial Language.

164
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:17,799
Mutual benefit.

165
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:19,519
I'll guarantee your escape.

166
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:26,679
Oh, so cooperating meant pretending
to be Golden Burial Attendants?

167
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,960
Why didn't you say so earlier?

168
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:30,239
So these are the ones who shed all
deathly aura,

169
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:33,039
able to walk under the sun—the Golden
Burial Attendants.

170
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,879
Calling this clan vengeful spirits

171
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:37,839
is less accurate than calling them
descendants of Demon Immortals.

172
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,959
The Ancient Burial Language...

173
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,400
Teach me the Ancient Burial Language.

174
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,919
Or we'll be exposed immediately.

175
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:48,959
I wondered why an Undying Medicine was
wandering alone out here.

176
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,039
Turns out it already had an owner.

177
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,919
Shen Ming, you're happy for nothing.

178
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,639
My name is San Zang (Three Stores).

179
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:58,119
May I ask how to address this Daoist
brother?

180
00:14:58,800 --> 00:14:59,800
I am Huang.

181
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,239
I was previously engrossed in appraising
treasure,

182
00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:02,959
and was careless, letting this medicine
escape.

183
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:04,719
So that's how it is.

184
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,639
I thought you were from outside the
domain.

185
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,839
Those guys get refined into burial
slaves, you know.

186
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:11,879
Interesting.

187
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,879
Such a unique aura.

188
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:17,759
Please, stop dawdling! Walk faster!

189
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:20,319
The most dangerous place is often the
safest.

190
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,239
Why don't we look around first,

191
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:24,400
swap out some burial artifacts,

192
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,839
and then play it by ear?

193
00:15:31,803 --> 00:15:36,183
